        <akn:num>29-406.31</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Standards of liability for directors.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_29-406_31_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>A director shall not be liable to the nonprofit corporation or its members for any decision to take or not to take action, or any failure to take any action, as a director, unless the party asserting liability in a proceeding establishes that:</akn:p></akn:content>
